# Implementation Plan - User Experience Improvements (Phase 5)

## Goal Description
Enhance the visual polish and perceived performance of the application. The immediate focus is on "Skeleton Loading" to replace blank screens during data fetching.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Implement Skeleton Loading
#### [NEW] [src/components/ui/Skeleton.tsx]
- Create a reusable `Skeleton` component (gray pulsing div) using Tailwind `animate-pulse`.

#### [NEW] [src/components/movies/MovieCardSkeleton.tsx]
- Create a mock version of `MovieCard` using skeletons for Poster, Title, and Year.

#### [MODIFY] [src/components/movies/MovieList.tsx]
- Update to show `MovieCardSkeleton` grid while `isLoading` is true.

#### [MODIFY] [src/pages/GenreList.tsx]
- Update to show skeletons while categories are loading.

## Verification Plan
1. **Throttling:** Use Chrome DevTools Network "Slow 3G".
2. **Visual Check:** refresh the page.
3. **Expectation:** See gray pulsing rectangles for 1-2 seconds before the actual usage loads, instead of a white flash or a tiny spinner.
